    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play the Free Demo Now!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting as a project for the 2023 Foddian Jam, Gooing Up! took second place in the developer vote, receiving copious praise for its charming aesthetic and intricately designed map. Since the game jam, we have polished and expanded Gooing Up! into a free demo with improved graphics, map design, sounds, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn your spot on the Demo Leaderboard today!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/ea9ff7b8599ed6c8db8eb00fea8ffebb.poster.avif?t=1741803784\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/ea9ff7b8599ed6c8db8eb00fea8ffebb.webm?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/ea9ff7b8599ed6c8db8eb00fea8ffebb.mp4?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast, Precise, Momentum-based Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Propel yourself using a rocket-jumping mechanic, then precisely control your movement mid-air with your projectile's kickback force. Time your shots carefully to navigate the labyrinthian goo factory with ease, and escape to the surface world!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/9def57cec5712e3a969b6081810d2c46.poster.avif?t=1741803784\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/9def57cec5712e3a969b6081810d2c46.webm?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/9def57cec5712e3a969b6081810d2c46.mp4?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a Non-Linear Map and Uncover its Secrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gooing Up! does not corral its players into a specific path, instead rewarding choice and exploration of its large, intricate map. Unlock cosmetics and achievements by performing optional challenges to climb in style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/6cdd0a4337e8b63086f86f32cc27d421.poster.avif?t=1741803784\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/6cdd0a4337e8b63086f86f32cc27d421.webm?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/6cdd0a4337e8b63086f86f32cc27d421.mp4?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Difficult but Fair</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only progression is the player's skill and knowledge. Learn the map by replaying sections in Training Mode to earn your place on the leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/368ac7dd1a6eba26721c7f0949b6b95b.poster.avif?t=1741803784\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/368ac7dd1a6eba26721c7f0949b6b95b.webm?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041720/extras/368ac7dd1a6eba26721c7f0949b6b95b.mp4?t=1741803784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Designed for Speedrunning and Casual Gaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gooing Up! is meant to be dissected and optimized by competitive players. The game contains high-score leaderboards, a training mode, and a non-linear map.</p>",
